                "imgDesc": "<p>The NRE (Menu 30), or \"Nutrition, Ready-to-Eat\" to use the full term, is a special item created by a certain alchemist. Completed dishes can be put inside this meal-in-a-pouch, to be ingested quickly under various circumstances. Tap to begin placing food inside.</p>",
